---
id: companies
---

%header
  .container
    %h1
      Companies

%section.section-gray
  .container
    %p.lead
      %strong
        Are you a Berlin-based company looking for freelance developers?
      %br
      Do you have trouble finding good candidates and does it seem like all the good developers are always busy? We can help!

%section
  .container
    .row

      .col-sm-6
        %p
          There are lots of freelance developers out there looking for new challenges. Through us you can find the candidates that perfectly match your requirements!
        %h3
          Why let Uplink find your next freelance developer?
        %ul
          %li
            = image_with_lazy_load image_path('icons/clock.svg')
            %strong
              Save time
            \- we know where to find the right candidates and can select those that match your professional requirements and price range.
          %li
            = image_with_lazy_load image_path('icons/wheelbarrow.svg')
            %strong
              Save money
            \- stop wasting money on developers that turn out to not be right for the job. We thoroughly vet each candidate and often know whether their previous clients were satisfied with their work.
        %p
          Fill out the form to the right to get started!

      .col-sm-6
        = form_tag t(:form_url) do
          = hidden_field_tag '_subject', value: 'New company'
          .form-group
            = label_tag 'name', caption: 'Your name'
            = text_field_tag 'name', id: 'name', class: 'form-control', required: true, placeholder: 'Jane Doe'
          .form-group
            = label_tag 'email', caption: 'Your email'
            = email_field_tag 'email', id: 'email', class: 'form-control', required: true, placeholder: 'your@email.com'
          .form-group
            = label_tag 'website', caption: 'Your website'
            = text_field_tag 'website', id: 'website', class: 'form-control', required: true, placeholder: 'www.yourcompany.com'
          .form-group
            = label_tag 'techs', caption: 'Which technologies do you work with?'
            = text_field_tag 'techs', id: 'techs', class: 'form-control', required: true, placeholder: 'Ruby, Rails, PHP, Node.js, ...'
          = submit_tag 'Submit', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary', data: { :'loading-text' => 'Please wait...' }
          %p.note
            We will keep all your data confidential, not create any profile page for your company, and never forward your data to anyone without your consent!
        .alert.alert-success
          Thanks! We'll be in touch with you shortly!
        .alert.alert-danger
          Uh-oh! Something went wrong... please try again!
